[gasp]

6
00:02:12,957 --> 00:02:16,424
Yes! There is
one left..!

7
00:02:17,891 --> 00:02:19,924
Oh! Tenten!

8
00:02:19,957 --> 00:02:21,557
Lee, you too?

9
00:02:23,757 --> 00:02:25,824
It's a good thing it
was you I ran into!

10
00:02:25,857 --> 00:02:29,224
Anyone else, and it
would've been a
serious tug-of-war.

11
00:02:29,257 --> 00:02:34,291
Agreed! Talk about good
luck-- Now we'll both be
able to read it! Here,
let me take a loo--

12
00:02:34,324 --> 00:02:34,891
[smack]

13
00:02:34,924 --> 00:02:36,624
What was that for?

14
00:02:36,657 --> 00:02:38,291
My question exactly!
Ladies first, Lee.

15
00:02:38,324 --> 00:02:40,924
You'll have to
wait until I'm
done with it!

16
00:02:40,957 --> 00:02:44,624
What the--!? You are
the one who is always
saying that gender
shouldn't matter!

17
00:02:44,657 --> 00:02:46,624
You're gonna read
it on the toilet..!

18
00:02:46,657 --> 00:02:49,324
So what!? You're
gonna read it in
the bath!

19
00:02:49,357 --> 00:02:51,291
Better than
stinking it up!

20
00:02:51,324 --> 00:02:53,757
I am not reading a
water damaged comic!

21
00:02:53,791 --> 00:02:57,757
oh would you let
go!? This issue
has info on the
movie!!

22
00:02:57,791 --> 00:03:00,324
I know! That is
exactly why--

23
00:03:00,357 --> 00:03:02,691
I want the latest
details now!!

24
00:03:03,991 --> 00:03:05,924
Ahhh!

25
00:03:13,357 --> 00:03:14,624
Huh?!

26
00:03:23,957 --> 00:03:26,457
"Road to Guy"

27
00:03:30,057 --> 00:03:31,491
[groan]

28
00:03:31,524 --> 00:03:34,224
What just happened?
It felt like the
world turned inside
out...

29
00:03:34,257 --> 00:03:38,724
Do not panic, Tenten!
Believe me, this has
happened before!

30
00:03:41,057 --> 00:03:44,091
[panting]

31
00:03:44,824 --> 00:03:47,157
Let us just stay calm
and find some water!

32
00:03:47,191 --> 00:03:50,357
No no no,
you just had
heat stroke.

33
00:03:50,391 --> 00:03:52,424
Hey, what are
you two doing
here?

34
00:03:52,457 --> 00:03:56,157
Shino? Boy, good
timing. Something
really weird just
happen--

35
00:03:56,524 --> 00:03:58,791
Not as weird as
your outfit!!!

36
00:03:58,824 --> 00:04:02,057
What do you mean
by that? I'm just
being FABULOUS as
usual.

37
00:04:02,091 --> 00:04:04,857
I may be a ninja
but I don't blend
into the background!

38
00:04:04,891 --> 00:04:06,291
That's the kinda
man I am!

39
00:04:06,324 --> 00:04:10,291
I am green with
envy! You are out-
pizazzing the star
of the show!

40
00:04:10,324 --> 00:04:14,491
Lee, you and Naruto
are all the pizazz
this show can handle.

41
00:04:15,091 --> 00:04:17,524
So like, did Shino
get a concussion or
something..?

42
00:04:17,557 --> 00:04:19,257
Don't...stare...

43
00:04:19,291 --> 00:04:20,057
Something wrong..?

44
00:04:20,091 --> 00:04:22,491
You're not usually
so shy, Kiba...

45
00:04:22,524 --> 00:04:23,757
Huh!?

46
00:04:23,791 --> 00:04:25,791
For goodness sake,
I'll answer for you!

47
00:04:25,824 --> 00:04:28,324
But don't think I'm
doing it to be nice
though, you guys!

48
00:04:28,357 --> 00:04:31,791
I can't depend on
anyone else here, so I
don't have a choice!

49
00:04:31,824 --> 00:04:33,391
Hinata is snapping
a people!?

50
00:04:33,424 --> 00:04:36,124
That's impossible!
What's wrong with
everyone!?

51
00:04:36,157 --> 00:04:37,257
<i>(Shikamaru)</i>
<i>There a problem?</i>

52
00:04:37,291 --> 00:04:38,257
-Huh!?
-Huh!?

53
00:04:39,191 --> 00:04:41,724
Shikamaru! Oh thank
goodness you're-- Huh!?

54
