whole world's gone
topsy turvy...

60
00:05:06,524 --> 00:05:10,057
I know what to
do! At times like
this, there's only
one way out!!

61
00:05:10,091 --> 00:05:10,757
Huh?

62
00:05:10,791 --> 00:05:12,724
Alrighty then.
Night-night.

63
00:05:14,224 --> 00:05:16,924
