dream Leeeeee!!

64
00:05:18,391 --> 00:05:19,224
Indeed.

65
00:05:19,257 --> 00:05:22,057
Be serious! This is
not a normal crisis!

66
00:05:22,091 --> 00:05:25,957
If we don't find
out what happened
we could be stuck
here forever!!

67
00:05:25,991 --> 00:05:27,757
Right! Let's
move out then!

68
00:05:27,791 --> 00:05:28,524
Where to?

69
00:05:28,557 --> 00:05:30,957
To find Neji!

70
00:05:30,991 --> 00:05:34,024
(Lee)
We will need help if
we are going to figure
out what happened!

71
00:05:34,257 --> 00:05:35,857
Yeah, but...

72
00:05:35,891 --> 00:05:40,724
It is okay! No matter
how much the world's
changed, our friendship
is unshakable!

73
00:05:42,924 --> 00:05:44,224
