We'll have to look
for clues on our own!

81
00:06:02,924 --> 00:06:05,857
(Hizashi Hyuga)
Neji, I'm leaving
your dinner out here!

82
00:06:11,557 --> 00:06:12,791
[gasp]

83
00:06:13,957 --> 00:06:16,391
