I am just realizing
something...

84
00:06:16,424 --> 00:06:17,957
What are you
talking about?

85
00:06:17,991 --> 00:06:20,124
I knew it!
Neji's ramen!

86
00:06:20,157 --> 00:06:22,157
<i>It is exactly</i>
<i>the same!</i>

87
00:06:22,191 --> 00:06:24,391
What?

88
00:06:24,424 --> 00:06:28,757
And the bizarre situation we've
found ourselves in, it's all
just like the promotional
material for the movie!

89
00:06:28,791 --> 00:06:30,791
So you're saying...

90
00:06:30,824 --> 00:06:34,424
I do not know
how or why...
but in that
instant...

91
00:06:35,291 --> 00:06:39,224
...our wish to know
what the movie would
be like was granted
by this issue of Jump!

92
00:06:39,257 --> 00:06:43,857
<i>Maybe we've been</i>
<i>transported into</i>
<i>the world of the</i>
<i>movie!</i>

93
00:06:43,891 --> 00:06:46,191
You really think
it's...possible?

94
00:06:48,391 --> 00:06:49,924
You ready, Tenten!?

95
00:06:49,957 --> 00:06:51,357
Let's do this, Lee!

96
00:06:51,391 --> 00:06:54,257
[grunts]

97
00:06:57,391 --> 00:06:58,857
How come it
didn't work?

98
00:06:58,891 --> 00:07:00,524
Everything was
exactly the same.

99
00:07:00,557 --> 00:07:03,024
No! One key element
was missing!

100
00:07:03,057 --> 00:07:04,357
Huh?

101
00:07:06,491 --> 00:07:08,724
<i>The first time, we both</i>
<i>longed to see the sneak</i>
<i>peek with every fiber</i>
<i>of our being!</i>

102
00:07:08,757 --> 00:07:13,224
<i>Our should burned with</i>
<i>passion, and we both</i>
<i>refused to let each other</i>
<i>have the first l</i>
ook!

103
00:07:13,257 --> 00:07:15,491
Like this!!

104
00:07:15,857 --> 00:07:19,391
Haaaaaaaaaaa!

105
