<i>(Tenten)</i>
<i>Cut it out! You're</i>
<i>going to rip it!</i>

106
00:07:26,024 --> 00:07:27,224
I am sorry...

107
00:07:27,257 --> 00:07:30,191
I hate to admit it,
but you might be
on to something...

108
00:07:30,224 --> 00:07:33,191
We can't just
follow a script,
though. We need
to FEEL it.

109
00:07:33,224 --> 00:07:34,991
A script...!?

110
00:07:35,024 --> 00:07:37,157
That is a
brilliant idea!

111
00:07:37,191 --> 00:07:39,991
What on earth are
you wearing...?

112
00:07:40,891 --> 00:07:44,824
I know just what to
do! Script revision
plan... go!

113
00:07:44,857 --> 00:07:46,357
Huh?

114
00:07:46,391 --> 00:07:50,257
If we do not have
enough passion, we
will just physically
alter the situation!

115
00:07:50,291 --> 00:07:54,024
That's way too
literal, Lee!
It'll never work!

116
00:07:54,891 --> 00:07:59,057
I will make it
work! I am not
staying in this
world another minute!

117
00:07:59,857 --> 00:08:03,524
<i>(Lee)</i>
<i>The Neji I know is</i>
<i>arrogant and wears</i>
<i>boxers...</i>

118
00:08:03,557 --> 00:08:05,791
<i>(Lee)</i>
<i>But he is also a</i>
<i>man who values</i>
<i>friendship!</i>

119
00:08:05,824 --> 00:08:07,791
<i>(Lee)</i>
<i>I am bringing</i>
<i>that Neji back!</i>

120
00:08:18,357 --> 00:08:20,857
